text:
Peaceful environment. Within 1km Schools - Nanyang Primary, Raffles Girls' Primary, Hwa Chong Institution, and nearby to Henry Park Primary.
Close proximity to Cold Storage Guthrie House , NTUC Fairprice Coronation Plaza, Cold Storage Specialty Greenwood. Short drive to F&B and vibrant entertainment options at GrandStand and Holland Village.

Nice place to live but SO FAR from public transport. Closest MRT Station is Tan Kah Kee, 1.2km away. Closest bus stop also 1.2km away.
Quiet location but dreadful if you don't have a car and don't want to spend all your wages on taxi / Uber.
Old and limited guest parking. But can park outside in landed area.
Beautiful condominium tucked away in a peaceful corner of Bukit Timah.
